metadata.name: BAMC Capital Membership #1
metadata.description:
NFT (Non-Fungible Token) is one of the most vibrant and dynamic sectors in the blockchain field. BAMC Capital focused on the blue-chip board of NFT sector, expecting to double the investors' returns in a year. 
Relying on the largest Chinese NFT community, BAMC NFT Club, BAMC Capital has a wide and strong influence in NFT sector. BAMC Capital is committed to providing financial support for the most promising and brilliant NFT projects, contributing to the colorful future of NFT.
